// desktop/renderer/trivia_roles.ts — P-TRIV.2 (ADR-0175): ROLE-AWARE question banks.
//
// The ADR-0088 onboarding role decides WHAT the Trivia Wire quizzes, so the game exercises the
// muscles each persona actually needs to keep warm (derisking skill/interest atrophy):
//   executive → GovCon market mechanics: M&A, opportunity vehicles, federal budget/priority dynamics
//   manager   → CMMI-DEV maturity level 3 + core project management
//   security  → CMMC 2.0 + NIST RMF
//   developer (or no role picked) → the general engineering seed bank (trivia_bank.ts)
//
// These are EVERGREEN fundamentals on purpose: a static bank cannot be "news". Live GovCon news
// quizzes and repo/prompt-tailored questions arrive with the generated packs (the ADR-0048
// checker-model pipeline, next increment) - which is also why every entry keeps the exact
// TriviaQuestion shape gated by isTriviaQuestion: generated role packs will pour through the same
// selection seam and fall back to THESE banks when malformed or unavailable.

